@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vyexwt(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = 0.65
    v2 = ((v0 - (v2 + 0.49 / v2 + 0.20)) - (wp.sin(v0 + 0.04) - v2))
    v2 = (0.32 / wp.abs((v0 + 0.42 * v0 + 0.96)))
    tmp = v1
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.cos(wp.abs(tmp + 0.32)))
    tmp = ((wp.sin(tmp + 0.42) * wp.cos(v0 + 0.80)) * tmp)
    data[tid] = v0
